{"tid":2440254,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"河北石家莊26層辦公大樓突發沖天大火","createTime":"2021-03-09T23:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T07:15:36.000Z","uid":41343,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"87fb620ec97b62b622c45657e2bf7be94c3cdfe5","tid":2440254,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T23:25:04.000Z","msg":"河北省石家莊市長安區眾鑫大廈周二（3月9日）上午11點左右發生火災，附近的主要交通路口已採取交通管制措施，石家莊消防已出動前往救援。目前明火基本被撲滅，為防止復燃，消防車仍在進行掃射滅火作業。在距離起火點不遠處，二十多輛寫著「橋西環衛」的工作車待命，為消防車源源不斷供水。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，此次火災燃燒的主要是保溫層。從石家莊市消防部門得到消息，火場無人受困。起火原因還在等待官方進一步的確認。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，眾鑫大廈2003年建成，只有1棟樓，共計622戶。大廈總高111.6米，共26層。大火從大廈一層燃起，據現場群眾反映，大火燃燒時曾聽到爆炸聲。"},{"pid":"d39a1072b233b963e9c86f268a69fc9da26c4b94","tid":2440254,"uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T23:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/d62be62f41a31b250debb2a85b7e608b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210309/_2021030915205849524.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2Fd62be62f41a31b250debb2a85b7e608b%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210309%2F_2021030915205849524.jpg&h=b6f59f3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"291c211f70d0b79c22f2a83a9b9ca81b88792a5d","tid":2440254,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T23:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/shvnfv2xnp6ZuwarltPR-5PI7ic=/535x356/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IU5T5QM7D5E7XMPPPBH3HXGOOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fshvnfv2xnp6ZuwarltPR-5PI7ic%3D%2F535x356%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIU5T5QM7D5E7XMPPPBH3HXGOOA.jpg&h=424c3e56&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0aee5579d3ebc202c432d1458ce264c448f4bf34","tid":2440254,"uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1